<item>
 <title>Sachi is Allergic to China</title>
 <link>http://theworldisnotflat.com/dispatch/2006/09/07/sachi-is-allergic-to-china</link>
 <description>  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;I do love my wife &amp;ndash; but she is such a huge nerd.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Did you know she has a degree in microbiology? You&amp;rsquo;d think with such knowledge, she would be more in tune with her own health.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Before we left, Sachi saw an allergist and learned that she has allergies to trees and grasses &amp;ndash; it affects her every year at home and her allergy medicine, which helps immensely, is in her backpack now.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Sometimes Sachi needs a reminder about this fact.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;For nearly the entire time that we&amp;rsquo;ve been in &lt;st1:country-region&gt;&lt;st1:place&gt;China&lt;/st1:place&gt;&lt;/st1:country-region&gt; so far (3 weeks) Sachi has had cold-like symptoms.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;In fact, I have acquired a cold and gotten over it while her symptoms persist.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Just today, I asked Sachi about the possibility of her symptoms being related to her allergies and a light bulb went on.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;After weeks of sneezing 50 times a day and wiping a chapped nose, the cure seemed so obvious &amp;ndash; in fact it was not much further than the pack on her back. As of this afternoon, Sachi has fully recovered from the &amp;ldquo;cold&amp;rdquo;, thanks to Zyrtec. DUH.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;I do not know why Sachi can&amp;rsquo;t recognize her own allergies, but I am now on allergy alert on her behalf.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Never again will I watch her suffer through weeks of a &amp;ldquo;cold&amp;rdquo; only to find that we&amp;rsquo;ve been sharing the room with the cure the whole time.&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;So much for microbiology.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;br class=&quot;clear&quot; /&gt;</description>
